text: Lea Lin Teutenberg (born 2 July 1999) is a German professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . Her father is Lars Teutenberg, her uncle Sven Teutenberg and her aunt Ina-Yoko Teutenberg. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:German female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
